# Susu Protocol — Git LFS routing
#
# The 60-90s demo video lives at apps/reference/public/demo.mp4. The repo
# currently ships a tiny placeholder file so the embed wires up cleanly;
# Story 8.6 adds this LFS attribute so when the real recording lands, it
# is routed through Git LFS instead of inflating git history.
*.mp4 filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
